metadata.name: Identity
metadata.description:
“Identity” is an artwork about different faces what we are wearing to hide our identity in this complex world.  Question is who is painting them.. is it your heart, your ego or manipulation by other masks. 

Technology advanced cyber girl on this artwork have decided to paint her own masks and maybe she is painting one for you…

Collaboration with Kiwami Artist

Created with Procreate  
Image size 5000x7000 pixels  
DPI 400
